               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, incomplete at the end</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="153v"/><title type="incomplete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <note>Due to the damage to the end of this codex, it is impossible to decipher further where the major works begin and end</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="133r"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2000Mazmur"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
